DIGEST
SB 186 Original 2026 Regular Session Fesi
Present law provides that anyone legally taking menhaden shall not have in their possession
more than five percent by weight of any species of fish other than menhaden and herring-like
species.
Proposed law retains present law and limits the total commercial menhaden reduction fishing
catch within Louisiana territorial waters to 315 million pounds.
Effective August 1, 2026.
(Amends R.S. 56:324)
